high_descs: Take a mug out of the fridge
Heat the mug in the microwave
Place the mug in the coffeemaker
anns.task_desc: Place a heated coffee mug in a coffeemaker

high_descs: Walk to the fridge on your left.
Grab a cup from the fridge and close it.
Walk to the kitchen stove behind you and to the right.
Put the cup in the microwave above the stove, then take it out.
Walk to the coffee maker on your right.
Put the cup under the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Warm a coffee mug for making coffee.

high_descs: Take a step left and forward to the fridge.
Take the mug out of the top part of the fridge.
Turn around and veer left to the microwave.
Heat the mug in the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the coffee maker on the left.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated mug in a coffee maker.
